      <label>Fig. 1.</label>
      <caption>
        <p>The screenshot of the POKY main window. (<bold>A</bold>) Main menu. (<bold>B</bold>) Pointer mode. (<bold>C</bold>) Tab widgets. (<bold>D</bold>) 3D structure calculation. (<bold>E</bold>) Spectral conversion, editing, visualization and text editing tools. (<bold>F</bold>) User support buttons. (<bold>G</bold>) Notification area</p>
      </caption>
      <graphic xlink:href="btab180f1" position="float"/>
